metadata.name: FFIntern Phunk
metadata.description: This is Johnny. All of his friends are gone, they didn't play video games or smoke pot. No, Johnny spent all his time wasting away like a typical degenerate video game junkie. One day Johnny met a human of the opposite sex. The did some weird horizontal jumping jacks, then the creature got large and pooped out a little eating machine that pooped and peed and made loud noises when everyone else tried to sleep. Now Johnny waits for his conviction In Ryan Cohen to pay off so he can finally wash this despair  and poverty away. Distracted by the lure of financial freedom and freedom of expression, Johnny has been lost in web3. Nothing in life worth doing was ever easy.
